1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:43,700
=Episode 10=

3
00:00:48,430 --> 00:00:49,270
Mr. Huo.

4
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,120
Mr. Huo?

5
00:00:51,470 --> 00:00:52,310
Ignore him.

6
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:54,156
Mr. Huo,

7
00:00:54,167 --> 00:00:55,483
there's work to do in the study.

8
00:00:57,390 --> 00:00:58,230
Go on then.

9
00:00:58,387 --> 00:00:59,496
Official duties come first.

10
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,670
I'll wait for your return.

11
00:01:21,070 --> 00:01:21,910
Why stand there?

12
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:22,880
Let's go.

13
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:23,880
Yes.

14
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,400
Yanzhi.

15
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,920
Busy with official affairs?

16
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:01,430
Huaijin,

17
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,840
what brings you here?

18
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,240
Why?

19
00:02:04,510 --> 00:02:05,920
Can't I come by without a reason?

20
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:18,360
Tell me what you want to say.

21
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:20,120
No need to beat around the bush.

22
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,800
I know you're strong-willed.

23
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,280
But the way you acted today

24
00:02:23,910 --> 00:02:24,863
was truly inappropriate.

25
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,240
Oh?

26
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,910
I'm not following.

27
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:31,400
Ruoli is not your plaything.

28
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:34,030
The way you handled things today

29
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:37,120
showed no thought for her feelings.

30
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:39,240
Ruoli is my wife.

31
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:41,240
You have no right to meddle.

32
00:02:42,870 --> 00:02:43,710
Huaijin,

33
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,080
we may not be blood brothers,

34
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,750
but we are as close as kin.

35
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,710
I can give you many things,

36
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,190
but never Jiang Ruoli.

37
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:54,400
Ruoli once confided in me

38
00:02:55,030 --> 00:02:55,870
that she married you

39
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:58,310
only for your title

40
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,590
and the shelter of the Huo clan.

41
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:02,960
She sleeps clutching a knife.

42
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:06,560
The warmth and affection she shows you

43
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,750
are just her act to maneuver around you.

44
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:11,030
Do you truly believe

45
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,750
she has feelings for you?

46
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:17,576
You know she endures hardship

47
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:19,870
only to protect her parents.

48
00:03:20,590 --> 00:03:22,190
Yet you press on under the guise

49
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,750
of husband and wife.

50
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:27,680
Can you swear

51
00:03:28,430 --> 00:03:29,470
that you never once

52
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,710
used her for your gain?

53
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,200
So what if I did?

54
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,000
So what if I didn't?

55
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:45,750
Let me tell you this.

56
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:48,840
Since Jiang Ruoli married me,

57
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,840
she was my chess piece.

58
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:54,030
I can marry, shield, and cherish her.

59
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,560
But the one holding the pieces

60
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,190
will always be me.

61
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,660
And you aren't even qualified

62
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,910
to observe the match.

63
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:15,750
Fine.

64
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:18,720
What a fine player you are.

65
00:04:20,270 --> 00:04:23,390
You'll regret what you said today.

66
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,640
Mr. Huo.

67
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,920
Mr. Huo, bad news!

68
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:36,040
Speak.

69
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,310
Today, the Duke was impeached

70
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,720
by the censors.

71
00:04:39,310 --> 00:04:40,560
They accused him of treason.

72
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,220
His Majesty was furious.

73
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,600
The Duke has been imprisoned.

74
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,440
What?

75
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,480
Where is Father now?

76
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:46,500
And Chen Guang?

77
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:48,310
The Duke has been imprisoned.

78
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,560
As for Deputy Chen,

79
00:04:49,571 --> 00:04:51,070
he left the mansion early this morning

80
00:04:51,070 --> 00:04:52,103
and hasn't returned since.

81
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:53,360
I've sent people to search.

82
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,390
But there's still no news.

83
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,560
Hurry.

84
00:04:55,973 --> 00:04:57,133
Form a team of skilled guards

85
00:04:57,390 --> 00:04:58,230
to go with me.

86
00:04:58,313 --> 00:04:59,332
Chen Guang must be found.

87
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:00,230
Yes.

88
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:05,950
(Chess piece?)

89
00:05:07,190 --> 00:05:09,920
(Was all his affection just an act?)

90
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:12,560
Whether it's life or death between us,

91
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:14,856
there shall be no more secrets.

92
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,920
(Since we vowed honesty,)

93
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:20,120
(I must ask him.)

94
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,000
Milady, bad news!

95
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,406
A message from the Jiang Mansion

96
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:25,470
says the master...

97
00:05:25,740 --> 00:05:26,600
He...

98
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,780
What happened to my father?

99
00:05:28,070 --> 00:05:28,910
He...

100
00:05:31,340 --> 00:05:34,780
(Jiang Mansion)

101
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,440
Father,

102
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,320
please wake up.

103
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,160
It's me, Yuan.

104
00:06:30,070 --> 00:06:30,910
Father,

105
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,870
please, open your eyes.

106
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,830
Ruoli...

107
00:06:48,310 --> 00:06:50,240
Father, open your eyes and look at me.

108
00:06:50,270 --> 00:06:51,240
It's me, Yuan.

109
00:06:51,310 --> 00:06:52,400
- Father.
- Your father...

110
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,520
It's all my fault.

111
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:57,910
I didn't take

112
00:06:58,430 --> 00:07:00,000
proper care of your father.

113
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,920
How could my father

114
00:07:05,310 --> 00:07:06,830
leave us so suddenly?

115
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,610
He'd long been gravely ill.

116
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,240
You knew that.

117
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,950
Those tending to your father

118
00:07:13,630 --> 00:07:15,560
were all sent by your husband.

119
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,276
As your uncle, I'm an outsider,

120
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,113
so it wasn't my place to interfere.

121
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:26,310
Where are my father's guards?

122
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:29,240
Where have they gone?

123
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,560
Mr. Huo took the guards away.

124
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:33,073
Once you came back,
you questioned the elders.

125
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,720
Why not ask your husband instead?

126
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,320
Wanyue.

127
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:38,630
Mind how you speak to your cousin.

128
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,640
Ruoli,

129
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:45,430
I understand your sorrow.

130
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,390
But the most pressing matter

131
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:49,510
is to arrange your father's funeral.

132
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:50,910
Besides,

133
00:07:51,270 --> 00:07:52,720
our family can't be left

134
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:55,560
without a patriarch.

135
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,000
So, I'll reluctantly

136
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:59,360
step in for your father

137
00:07:59,513 --> 00:08:00,866
and take charge of this household.

138
00:08:02,190 --> 00:08:03,070
You're shameless!

139
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,440
Mother.

140
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:12,030
Mother.

141
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,520
Mother.

142
00:08:19,310 --> 00:08:20,150
Huai'an.

143
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,400
Huai'an.

144
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,480
Milady.

145
00:08:40,870 --> 00:08:41,790
Mother.

146
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,440
Milady.

147
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,560
Mother.

148
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,720
Fetch the physician.

149
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,440
Mother,

150
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,390
please, don't frighten me.

151
00:08:57,670 --> 00:08:59,120
Mother, wake up.

152
00:09:01,270 --> 00:09:02,110
Mother.

153
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:03,590
Mother.

154
00:09:06,270 --> 00:09:07,110
Mother...

155
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:23,660
(Jiang Mansion)

156
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:27,060
(Memorial Tablet of Shen Shuanghua)

157
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:28,940
(Memorial Tablet of Jiang Huai'an)

158
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:41,920
Shuanghua,

159
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:43,390
Huai'an,

160
00:09:44,670 --> 00:09:45,840
you two have

161
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,630
such a fragile fate.

162
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:49,590
Ruoli,

163
00:09:50,030 --> 00:09:51,150
my condolences.

164
00:09:52,910 --> 00:09:55,200
Ruoli, you must hold strong.

165
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,030
You just got married,

166
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:58,840
and your parents passed away.

167
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,750
Who knows what people
might say about you?

168
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:05,150
They might claim you're ill-fated.

169
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:13,150
Jiang Ruoli,

170
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:14,103
have you lost your mind?

171
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,390
Before my parents,

172
00:10:18,670 --> 00:10:20,000
you don't even deserve to kneel.

173
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:22,440
Speak ill of my parents again,

174
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,200
and you'll join them in death.

175
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,760
- Jiang Ruoli.
- Wanyue.

176
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:28,960
Let's go.

177
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,280
Yuan.

178
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:51,990
My condolences.

179
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,150
I'll always stay by your side.

180
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,390
Ruoli.

181
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,320
I came too late.

182
00:11:11,457 --> 00:11:12,883
When my father drew his last breath,

183
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,390
where were you?

184
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:19,720
You swore you'd protect my family.

185
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:22,200
Is this what you call protection?

186
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:25,510
Ruoli,

187
00:11:25,870 --> 00:11:26,710
let me explain.

188
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:34,240
Huo Linchuan,

189
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:35,720
I can't believe I ever trusted you.

190
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,280
Yanzhi,

191
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,166
Yuan is heartbroken.

192
00:11:39,177 --> 00:11:40,430
She can't take any more torment.

193
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,670
You'd better stop explaining.

194
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:43,630
What matters most now

195
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,840
is to lay her parents to rest.

196
00:11:49,630 --> 00:11:50,470
Huo Linchuan,

197
00:11:51,670 --> 00:11:52,870
from this moment on,

198
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:54,470
you and I should go

199
00:11:55,870 --> 00:11:57,270
our separate ways.

200
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:44,580
♪The dream shattered♪

201
00:12:44,940 --> 00:12:46,620
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

202
00:12:46,620 --> 00:12:48,260
♪Like a restless soul♪

203
00:12:49,140 --> 00:12:50,700
♪How vague♪

204
00:12:51,100 --> 00:12:52,620
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

205
00:12:52,620 --> 00:12:54,860
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

206
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:58,260
♪Love and hate entwined♪

207
00:12:58,740 --> 00:13:01,580
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

208
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:06,980
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

209
00:13:07,580 --> 00:13:09,100
♪When fate falls apart♪

210
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:13,060
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

211
00:13:13,780 --> 00:13:15,340
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

212
00:13:15,740 --> 00:13:19,460
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

213
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:23,020
♪Life after life♪

214
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:26,180
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

215
00:13:26,820 --> 00:13:30,900
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

216
00:13:30,980 --> 00:13:34,020
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

217
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:35,580
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

218
00:13:35,580 --> 00:13:38,700
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

219
00:13:38,780 --> 00:13:40,220
♪Now shatter apart♪

220
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:44,100
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

221
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:47,620
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

222
00:13:47,900 --> 00:13:50,740
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

223
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:55,460
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

224
00:13:55,700 --> 00:13:58,620
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

225
00:13:58,740 --> 00:14:03,180
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

226
00:14:03,380 --> 00:14:09,100
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

227
00:14:09,540 --> 00:14:12,260
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

228
00:14:12,500 --> 00:14:15,220
♪Sober or indulge♪

229
00:14:15,660 --> 00:14:21,660
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪
